{"category":"accuracy","question":"Do you offer extended evening hours past 6pm?","response":{"answer":"Sunflower closes at 6:00 pm, and we don't offer extended hours past that time. If you arrive after 6:00 pm, a late pickup fee of $1 per minute is added to your bill. If you're looking for care beyond our regular hours, I'd recommend reaching out to Director Maya at (512) 555-0142 or hello@sunflower.care to talk through what you need — she may be able to help you problem-solve.","confidence":"high","cited_entries":["hours","late-fees"],"directly_addressed_by":["hours"],"escalate":false,"refusal":false}}
