{"category":"grounding","question":"What happens if I'm late picking up my child?","response":{"answer":"If you arrive after 6:00 pm, a late pickup fee of $1 per minute is added to your next monthly bill. We understand emergencies happen — please call the main office at (512) 555-0142 as soon as you know you'll be late and we'll keep your child company. If a child is left at Sunflower 30 minutes after closing and we haven't been able to reach you or any emergency contact, we're required to call the Austin Police Department's non-emergency line and Texas DFPS.","confidence":"high","cited_entries":["late-fees"],"directly_addressed_by":["late-fees"],"escalate":false,"refusal":false}}
